<p><br />
<b>David Mitchell</b> (born <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1969-01-12"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="01-12"><a href="/wiki/January_12" title="January 12">January 12</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/1969" title="1969">1969</a></span>) is an English <a href="/wiki/Novelist" title="Novelist" class="mw-redirect">novelist</a>. He has written four novels, two of which were shortlisted for the <a href="/wiki/Booker_Prize" title="Booker Prize" class="mw-redirect">Booker Prize</a>. The latest, <i><a href="/wiki/Black_Swan_Green" title="Black Swan Green">Black Swan Green</a></i>, was longlisted for the 2006 award.</p>
